    {
      "id": "PopularPost367402",
      "post_content": "I'm mainly an EDH player, and I've put together a deck list with 41 enchantments to make this card go crazy. Obvious inclusions, Paradox Haze for double the pleasure, Form of the Dragon, Dovescape and Phyrexian Unlife to never die, and a bunch of other cheeky pieces as well. My win-con is Eidolon of Countless Battles from Born of the Gods, slapped with an Ethereal Armor and Daybreak Coronet.  \nSome of the cheeky enchantments are auras that steal permanents. There are also a bunch of non-enchantment pieces to help fish out pieces I need; tutors and creatures like Academy Rector.  \n I'm excited to get all the pieces together and test it out.",
      "posted_by": "kor6sic6",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost367402\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_post\">I'm mainly an EDH player, and I've put together a deck list with 41 enchantments to make this card go crazy. Obvious inclusions, Paradox Haze for double the pleasure, Form of the Dragon, Dovescape and Phyrexian Unlife to never die, and a bunch of other cheeky pieces as well. My win-con is Eidolon of Countless Battles from Born of the Gods, slapped with an Ethereal Armor and Daybreak Coronet.<br/>Some of the cheeky enchantments are auras that steal permanents. There are also a bunch of non-enchantment pieces to help fish out pieces I need; tutors and creatures like Academy Rector.<br/> I'm excited to get all the pieces together and test it out.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '367402'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy60748\">kor6sic6</span>\r\n                                (3/12/2014 9:51:01 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_po